publication was previously available only in print media  and now is available below  There are 2 editions of Job Choices tailored to your interests       Job Choices   Job Choices Diversity Edition  You can also find the following critical job information in Job Choices    Adapting to corporate culture  Advice on using social networking in the job search  Career fair connections  From student to professional  Information for going on to graduate school  Professional dress  Tips for the successful interviewing  The art of writing job search letters  Your rights and responsibilities as a job seeker  USA Jobs  Work For America  Workplace e Etiquette    VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 